com.mashery.http

Interface HTTPHeaders

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Iterable<String>, ParamGroup
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    MutableHTTPHeaders

    public interface HTTPHeaders
extends ParamGroup
    Represents HTTP message headers as a parameter group with case-insensitive name lookup. Values returned by ParamGroup.get(String) belong the last header with the matching name.
    Restriction
    This interface is not intended to be implemented by clients.
    Restriction
    This interface is not intended to be extended by clients.

      • getElements

        HTTPHeaderElements getElements(String name)
        Returns elements for the last header with the given name. The elements are parsed from the header's (presumably appropriately structured) value. Returns null if there is no header with that name.
        Parameters:
        name - header name
        Returns:
        elements for the last header with the given name, or null
